title: Additional ANA Charter in October 2015: Matsuyama – Taipei Song Shan
text:
Additional ANA Charter in October 2015: Matsuyama – Taipei Song Shan   
Sep 23, 2015 eTN   
In October 2015, ANA plans to operate two round-trip charter services on Matsuyama – Taipei Song Shan route with a Boeing 767-300ER aircraft. Planned service is scheduled on 00 October 2015 and 12 October 2015. In Chinese writing, Matsuyama and Song Shan shares the identical character “松山”. 
09OCT15
